translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お好きにどうぞ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Do as you like.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・・ま、違うのは分かっているけどな。はぁ・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Well, I know it's different, but still. Sigh...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エロを見ていない場合
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you haven't seen the erotic scenes,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やはり私が疑われているのですね・・・なんかどんよりしている。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It seems I'm still being suspected... It's kind of gloomy.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 疑われている事、アリオスの事、ともに解決していない状態です
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Being suspected, the matter with Arios, both remain unresolved.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アリオスとはどんな関係なんだ・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What kind of relationship do you have with Arios?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それは・・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That is...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レイの元から脱出したのは、その　あっ、わかった、君みたいな美人だから
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I escaped from Demon Ray because, um, ah, I got it—it's because you're a beautiful woman like him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 言えません
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I can't say.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・・・うーん
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Hmm.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 明日の戦いはこの命を自由都市地域を守る為にさざけるつもりです。それで真実を証明したい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Tomorrow's battle, I intend to risk this life to protect the Free City region. That way, I want to prove the truth.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うむむ、セシルちゃんはうまく落とせるはずだったのだが、なんかタイミングを逸してしまったな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, I should have been able to win over Cecil-chan smoothly, but somehow I missed the timing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ま、それでもこの子が内通者とはとても思えない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, even so, I can't possibly think this girl is a traitor.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスと直接面談です。二人っきり
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A direct meeting with Rance. Just the two of us.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 話す内容はキャラによって違います
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The contents of the conversation differ depending on the character.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスと直接面談です。二人っきり
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A direct meeting with Rance. Just the two of us.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 話す内容はキャラによって違います
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The contents of the conversation differ depending on the character.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 面談が終わった・・夜も遅い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The meeting is over... It's late at night.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そろそろ眠い、セックスでもしてた方がいいと思うランス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm getting sleepy, Rance thinks it might be better to have sex or something.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス、シィル、かなみ、サテラ、ミラクル、ベゼルアイ、など主要メンバー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Main members like Rance, Shiru, Kanami, Satera, Miracle, Bezel Eye, and others.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: さて、どうするかだが・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well then, what to do...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス様、裏切り者わかりましたか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lord Rance, have you found out who the traitor is?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ふふふ、そうだな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hehehe, that's right.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞選択
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Select

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　１回目の面談で選んだ人
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > The person chosen in the first meeting

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　２回目の面談で選んだ人
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > The person chosen in the second meeting

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　３回目の面談で選んだ人
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > The person chosen in the third meeting

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 分かったというランス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance says he understands.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やっぱり内通者が居るのですか？誰ですか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: So there really is a traitor? Who is it?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今回、面談した者の中に居るのですか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Is it someone among those we interviewed this time?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's right.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だとしてら・・ＸＸＸかＸＸＸかＸＸＸ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If so... it's either XXX, XXX, or XXX.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この３人のうち誰か・・誰ですか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: One of these three... who is it?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 内緒だ、向こうに悟られてはまずいからな。当日のお楽しみだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's a secret; it would be bad if the other side finds out. Look forward to the day.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もう一度　ｉｆ　ビヨンホウが怪しい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Once again, if Biyonhou is suspicious.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうだな、かなみ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's right, Kanami.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: かなみに別命を与える、それを聞いたかなみ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kanami is given a separate order, and she hears it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ええ、確かにＭランドにみなさんいると思いますが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, I believe everyone is indeed at M-Land.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いいから急げ、今夜中だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Just hurry, it has to be done tonight.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: わかったわとかなみ旅立つ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kanami says, 'Understood,' and sets off on her journey.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今夜は徹夜だな、世界を牛耳る総統閣下は忙しいな。にやにや
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's an all-nighter tonight, the Supreme Leader who controls the world is busy. Hehehe.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どうでしたランス様
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: How was it, Lord Rance?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うーん、なんかピンとこない。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, something doesn't quite click.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どいつも内通者じゃない気がする。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I feel like none of them are the traitor.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うーん、面倒だ、もう寝る。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, it's troublesome, I'm going to sleep now.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なーに、少々裏切り者が居ても俺様のパワーで押し切って勝てばよいのだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, even if there are a few traitors, I can push through and win with my power.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: よく朝、セキガハラ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Good morning, Sekigahara.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物大将軍ピサロの司令部、コンバートも居る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At Demon General Pizarro's headquarters, Convert is also present.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 内通は予定通りです、絶対に成功します。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The betrayal is going as planned; it will definitely succeed.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 失敗したら私殺してもらってもいいですよとか自信満々
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Confidently saying, 'If I fail, you can kill me if you want.'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レイが現れる、今日まで戦うの我慢してやったんだ、今日は思う存分していいんだろうな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon Ray appears, saying he’s been holding back fighting until today, so today he can go all out, right?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もちろんです、あなたの狙うカオスを持つ人類側の特別部隊もここに居ますよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Of course, the special human forces targeting Chaos that you aim for are also here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ここ、魔人レイが前にカオスに刺されて重傷を負い、その怪我が治っていない事を入れて下さい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Here, please include that Demon Ray was previously stabbed by Chaos and is seriously injured, and that wound hasn't healed.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この程度いいハンデだとか言っている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He says that this level of handicap is no big deal.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ただ、この旗印をかかげる人間の部隊は無視して下さい、我々の仲間になります。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, please ignore the human units bearing this flag; they are our allies.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: めんどくせぇな、全部殺せばいいのに
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What a pain, they should just kill them all.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人類側、ランスが起きた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: On the human side, Rance has awakened.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お好きにどうぞ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Do as you like.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・・ま、違うのは分かっているけどな。はぁ・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Well, I know it's different, but still. Sigh...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エロを見ていない場合
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you haven't seen the erotic scenes,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やはり私が疑われているのですね・・・なんかどんよりしている。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It seems I'm still being suspected... It's kind of gloomy.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 疑われている事、アリオスの事、ともに解決していない状態です
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Being suspected, the matter with Arios, both remain unresolved.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アリオスとはどんな関係なんだ・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What kind of relationship do you have with Arios?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それは・・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That is...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レイの元から脱出したのは、その　あっ、わかった、君みたいな美人だから
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I escaped from Demon Ray because, um, ah, I got it—it's because you're a beautiful woman like him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 言えません
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I can't say.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・・・うーん
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Hmm.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 明日の戦いはこの命を自由都市地域を守る為にさざけるつもりです。それで真実を証明したい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Tomorrow's battle, I intend to risk this life to protect the Free City region. That way, I want to prove the truth.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うむむ、セシルちゃんはうまく落とせるはずだったのだが、なんかタイミングを逸してしまったな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, I should have been able to win over Cecil-chan smoothly, but somehow I missed the timing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ま、それでもこの子が内通者とはとても思えない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, even so, I can't possibly think this girl is a traitor.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスと直接面談です。二人っきり
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A direct meeting with Rance. Just the two of us.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 話す内容はキャラによって違います
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The contents of the conversation differ depending on the character.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスと直接面談です。二人っきり
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A direct meeting with Rance. Just the two of us.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 話す内容はキャラによって違います
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The contents of the conversation differ depending on the character.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 面談が終わった・・夜も遅い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The meeting is over... It's late at night.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そろそろ眠い、セックスでもしてた方がいいと思うランス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm getting sleepy, Rance thinks it might be better to have sex or something.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス、シィル、かなみ、サテラ、ミラクル、ベゼルアイ、など主要メンバー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Main members like Rance, Shiru, Kanami, Satera, Miracle, Bezel Eye, and others.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: さて、どうするかだが・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well then, what to do...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス様、裏切り者わかりましたか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lord Rance, have you found out who the traitor is?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ふふふ、そうだな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hehehe, that's right.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞選択
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Select

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　１回目の面談で選んだ人
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > The person chosen in the first meeting

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　２回目の面談で選んだ人
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > The person chosen in the second meeting

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　３回目の面談で選んだ人
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > The person chosen in the third meeting

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 分かったというランス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance says he understands.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やっぱり内通者が居るのですか？誰ですか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: So there really is a traitor? Who is it?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今回、面談した者の中に居るのですか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Is it someone among those we interviewed this time?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's right.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だとしてら・・ＸＸＸかＸＸＸかＸＸＸ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If so... it's either XXX, XXX, or XXX.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この３人のうち誰か・・誰ですか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: One of these three... who is it?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 内緒だ、向こうに悟られてはまずいからな。当日のお楽しみだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's a secret; it would be bad if the other side finds out. Look forward to the day.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もう一度　ｉｆ　ビヨンホウが怪しい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Once again, if Biyonhou is suspicious.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうだな、かなみ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's right, Kanami.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: かなみに別命を与える、それを聞いたかなみ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kanami is given a separate order, and she hears it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ええ、確かにＭランドにみなさんいると思いますが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, I believe everyone is indeed at M-Land.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いいから急げ、今夜中だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Just hurry, it has to be done tonight.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: わかったわとかなみ旅立つ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kanami says, 'Understood,' and sets off on her journey.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今夜は徹夜だな、世界を牛耳る総統閣下は忙しいな。にやにや
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's an all-nighter tonight, the Supreme Leader who controls the world is busy. Hehehe.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どうでしたランス様
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: How was it, Lord Rance?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うーん、なんかピンとこない。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, something doesn't quite click.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どいつも内通者じゃない気がする。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I feel like none of them are the traitor.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うーん、面倒だ、もう寝る。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, it's troublesome, I'm going to sleep now.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なーに、少々裏切り者が居ても俺様のパワーで押し切って勝てばよいのだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, even if there are a few traitors, I can push through and win with my power.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: よく朝、セキガハラ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Good morning, Sekigahara.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物大将軍ピサロの司令部、コンバートも居る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At Demon General Pizarro's headquarters, Convert is also present.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 内通は予定通りです、絶対に成功します。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The betrayal is going as planned; it will definitely succeed.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 失敗したら私殺してもらってもいいですよとか自信満々
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Confidently saying, 'If I fail, you can kill me if you want.'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レイが現れる、今日まで戦うの我慢してやったんだ、今日は思う存分していいんだろうな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon Ray appears, saying he’s been holding back fighting until today, so today he can go all out, right?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もちろんです、あなたの狙うカオスを持つ人類側の特別部隊もここに居ますよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Of course, the special human forces targeting Chaos that you aim for are also here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ここ、魔人レイが前にカオスに刺されて重傷を負い、その怪我が治っていない事を入れて下さい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Here, please include that Demon Ray was previously stabbed by Chaos and is seriously injured, and that wound hasn't healed.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この程度いいハンデだとか言っている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He says that this level of handicap is no big deal.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ただ、この旗印をかかげる人間の部隊は無視して下さい、我々の仲間になります。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, please ignore the human units bearing this flag; they are our allies.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: めんどくせぇな、全部殺せばいいのに
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What a pain, they should just kill them all.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人類側、ランスが起きた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: On the human side, Rance has awakened.
